data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and character in this beautiful 3-bedroom residence. Nestled in the heart of Chehalis, this home offers you a fresh start with incredible updates and renovations throughout.  New roof, new windows, new flooring, new fridge, new washer/dryer, and new range in the kitchen.  The entire home has been re-plumbed to ensure a seamless and reliable water flow.  Large corner lot with stucco exterior and courtyard with outdoor fireplace.  Full basement with tons of storage space, and two garages.
